				<strong>Web Programming</strong> <br><span class="text-sm">also love in travel activity and being a Videographer </span></div>
		</div>
		</header>
		<!-- about me -->
		<div class="about my-5" id="about">
			<br>
			<h2 class="text-center mt-18 mb-1"><span class="font-extrabold text-transparent text-2xl bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-200"
				>About</span> Me</h2>
			<div class="subcard flex justify-center w-100 mb-5">
				<SubCard/>
			</div>
			<h3 class="font-bold">Education</h3>
